              "path": [ "api", "import", "orders" ]
            },
            "description": "Multipart upload. Provide at least one of the file fields `xml` and/or `json`. Each is schema-validated, and valid documents are persisted. Returns per-file results plus `allValid` (200 if all valid, 422 otherwise). Requires FULL.\n\nNote: Postman cannot embed file contents, so the file paths point at backend/samples/. If your machine differs, re-select the files in the Body tab."
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
